# Home Assistant Add-on: Globalping Probe

[![Release][release-shield]][release] ![Project Stage][project-stage-shield] ![Project Maintenance][maintenance-shield]

Run a Globalping network probe on Home Assistant.

## About

This add-on packages the upstream [Globalping probe][probe] for use as a
Home Assistant Supervisor add-on. Once running, your Home Assistant host
joins the Globalping network and can answer measurement requests
(`ping`, `traceroute`, `mtr`, `dns`, `http`) from its location.

